Posts.Content: If you are having a gut feeling, I agree that you should go to the doctor sooner than later, if for nothing else, some peace of mind. Please let us know how it turns out, I really pray that it turns out to be nothing.  PS Here's a site that really exhausts the signs and symptoms: http://www.wellsphere.com/breast-cancer-article/signs-sympto  Andrea
Posts.Title: After 36 years, I'm worried again
